Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Superman Hold
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Lie on your stomach and lift arms and legs simultaneously, holding the position.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Reverse Plank
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Support your weight with arms behind you and keep your body in a straight line.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Bridge Hold
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Push your hips and chest upwards, holding a bridge position.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Shoulder Dislocates
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Use a wide grip to bring your arms overhead and behind your back for shoulder mobility.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Wall Walks
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Start facing a wall and walk your hands down into a bridge position.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Prone Y Raises
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Lie face down, lift your arms into a Y shape, and squeeze your upper back.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Cobra Stretch
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Lie on your stomach and push up with your hands to extend your back.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Table Bridge
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Sit with feet and hands on the floor, push hips up into a table position.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Wall Shoulder Stretch
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Press hands against a wall and lean forward to stretch shoulders and upper back.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Cat-Cow Stretch
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Move between arching and rounding your back for spinal flexibility.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Elbow Bridge
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Perform a bridge while supporting yourself on your elbows.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Standing Backbend
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Stand upright and bend backward while engaging your core.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Wall Bridge
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Perform a bridge with your feet against a wall to increase back flexibility.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Hindu Push-Ups
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Start in a downward dog position, swoop down, and push back up.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Seated Forward Fold
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Sit with legs extended and reach forward to stretch your back and hamstrings.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Wall Shoulder Openers
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Face a wall, place hands overhead, and lean forward for a deep shoulder stretch.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Wrist Extensions
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Stretch your wrists to improve flexibility for bridges and arm stands.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Superman Lifts
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Lie on your stomach and lift your upper body and legs repeatedly.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Back Extension Holds
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Hold a back extension position while lying on your stomach.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Dynamic Backbends
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Move in and out of a backbend for mobility and control.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Reverse Snow Angels
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Lie face down and move arms in a snow angel motion for back mobility.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Scapular Wall Slides
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Slide your arms up and down a wall to activate your shoulder mobility.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Thoracic Bridge
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Perform a bridge focusing on upper back extension.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Quadruped T-Spine Rotations
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Start on all fours, rotate one arm upward, then switch sides.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Downward Dog to Cobra Flow
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Transition between downward dog and cobra stretch to open the back.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Back Roll to Bridge
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Roll backward onto your shoulders and transition into a bridge.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Neck Bridges
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Lie on your back and press through your neck to lift your upper body.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Arm Circles
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Rotate your arms forward and backward to warm up shoulders.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Pelvic Tilts
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Gently tilt your pelvis forward and backward to warm up the lower back.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Hip Bridges
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Push hips up while lying down to activate lower back and glutes.

Back Strengthening & Mobility.name: Wrist Flexor Stretch
Back Strengthening & Mobility.description: Extend your arm and pull back on your fingers to stretch the wrist flexors.
